V0504_01_00_00_0.text: You're the perfect victim to test my new deck!

V0504_01_00_01_0.text: Witness the skills that pay the bills and give the thrills!

V0504_01_00_01_1.text:
Let's give it up for Sylvio!
...Heh! Nailed it!

V0504_01_00_02_0.text:
I'm Sylvio Sawatari!
Or better known as today's main event!

V0504_01_00_03_0.text: I don't want a bad review, so don't ruin my show!

V0504_01_00_04_0.text:
Don't settle for fakes!
My Dueltaining is the real deal!

V0504_01_00_05_0.text: I'll play the role of the winner and you play the loser!

V0504_01_00_06_0.text: Let's decide which of us deserves to run the city!

V0504_03_00_00_0.text: You've realized how great I am a tad too late!

V0504_03_00_01_0.text: It's the final act of my showstopping performance!

V0504_03_00_02_0.text:
What's more perfect than perfect?
My Dueling!

V0504_03_00_05_0.text: I think I've given you enough of a head start!

V0504_05_00_00_0.text:
You're playing great.
But in this Duel, I'm the headliner!

V0504_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my Set card!

V0504_10_00_02_0.text: Things are about to get more exciting!

V0504_11_01_00_0.text: I summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0504_11_08_01_0.text:
I build the Overlay Network!
Xyz Summon!

V0504_11_09_01_0.text:
I Pendulum Summon!
My monsters can swing into action too!

V0504_16_00_00_0.text: We've reached the climax of this spectacular spectacular!

V0504_16_00_02_0.text: When I finish you, you'll have exactly 0 LP!

V0504_21_00_00_0.text: The crowd will be bored if I win too easily!

V0504_21_00_01_0.text: There's a reason why I was cast as the hero instead of you!

V0504_21_00_02_0.text: Some enjoy quick matches - I like savoring mine!

V0504_21_00_04_0.text: Humph! I'll finish you on my next turn!

V0504_21_00_05_0.text: Stop making moves that I didn't expect!

V0504_28_00_00_0.text: Don't blame my monsters for your defeat.

V0504_28_00_01_0.text: Who has the best strategies and the fastest reactions?

V0504_28_00_02_0.text: I was expected to win... and I did!

V0504_28_00_02_1.text: Because there's no Duelist stronger than Sylvio!

V0504_28_00_04_0.text:
Woohoo!
I got you good!
Oh yeah!

V0504_28_00_05_0.text: While I shine like a star, you're stuck in the mud!

V0504_28_00_06_0.text:
Ha!
Everyone loves me!
Even my cards love me!

V0504_28_00_07_0.text: You need higher quality cards in your deck.

V0504_29_00_00_0.text:
How humiliating...
You'll pay for this a hundred times over!

V0504_29_00_01_0.text:
I'm the star, not you!
Stop stealing the spotlight!

V0504_29_00_03_0.text: Since when was I the supporting role?

V0504_29_00_04_0.text:
Argh!
I was so close to winning!

V0504_29_00_05_0.text: It's annoying because you're not a better Duelist than me!

V0504_29_00_06_0.text: I'm going to report you to my Pop!

V0504_33_00_00_0.text: Sylvio's here to present Dueltaining at its finest!

V0504_33_00_02_0.text: Spoiler alert! I'm going to win!

V0504_33_00_03_0.text: Here's how I swing into action!

V0504_30_00_00_0.text: I'm pretty good, if I do say so myself!

V0504_30_00_01_0.text:
Ha!
Why would you play a card that weak?

V0504_30_00_02_0.text:
Poor you...
You don't have the cards you need.

V0504_34_00_00_0.text: For all the hype, I thought you'd play something stronger!

V0504_34_00_01_0.text: Stop firing up the crowd! That's my job!

V0504_34_00_02_0.text: Unless you can defeat me in one turn, you're easy pickings!

V0504_34_00_03_0.text: The spectators are loving our Duel!

V0504_34_00_04_0.text: All eyes are on you. Can you live up to the moment?

V0504_34_00_05_0.text: That's not how you're supposed to play that card.

V0504_34_00_07_0.text: I only have rare cards in my deck - no weak ones!

V0504_34_00_08_0.text: I don't know that card - because it's so weak!

V0504_34_00_09_0.text: I'm going to complain about you to my Pop!

V0504_34_00_11_0.text: I've upgraded to Neo New Sylvio!

V0504_35_00_00_0.text: Sylvio is the true star of the show!

V0504_35_00_01_0.text:
No problem!
Leave it to Sylvio to save the day!

V0504_36_00_00_0.text: You and I are in sync!

V0504_36_00_01_0.text: We make a pretty good team!

V0504_36_00_02_0.text: Make sure you do your share!

V0504_36_00_04_0.text: Hey! You can at least try helping out!

V0504_36_00_05_0.text:
Fine! I'll let you have the spotlight!
So do something!

V0504_08_00_00_0.text: I play the Field Spell, Abyss Playhouse - Fantastic Theater!

V0504_08_00_02_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Abyss Script - Opening Ceremony!

V0504_08_00_03_0.text: Ha! By destroying Opening Ceremony, you set off its effect!

V0504_08_00_04_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Abyss Script - Fantasy Magic!

V0504_08_00_05_0.text: You destroyed Abyss Script - Fantasy Magic!

V0504_08_00_05_1.text: When this Set card is destroyed, its effect activates!

V0504_08_00_06_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Abyss Script - Fire Dragon's Lair!

V0504_08_00_07_0.text: You destroyed Fire Dragon's Lair, so its effect activates!

V0504_08_00_08_0.text:
I activate my Spell!
Abyss Script - Rise of the Abyss King!

V0504_08_00_09_0.text:
You destroyed Rise of the Abyss King!
Its effect activates!

V0504_08_00_10_0.text: I play the Continuous Spell, Abyss Script - Abysstainment!

V0504_08_00_12_0.text: Abysstainment's effect activates when it's destroyed!

V0504_08_00_13_0.text: I play the Quick-Play Spell, Abyss Script - Romantic Terror!

V0504_08_00_14_0.text: Thanks! By destroying Romantic Terror, its effect activates!

V0504_08_00_15_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Spell!
Abyss Prop - Wild Wagon!

V0504_08_00_16_1.text: Abyss Prop - Wild Wagon's effect activates!

V0504_08_00_17_0.text: When Wild Wagon is destroyed, its effect activates!

V0504_08_00_18_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Abyss Actors Back Stage!

V0504_08_00_19_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Abyss Actors' Curtain Call!

V0504_08_00_20_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Spell!
Yosen Training Grounds!

V0504_08_00_22_0.text: Allow me to present my legendary combo!

V0504_08_00_22_1.text: I play the Continuous Trap, Dizzying Winds of Yosen Village!

V0504_08_00_23_0.text: This Duel is blowing my way!

V0504_08_00_23_1.text: I activate the Continuous Spell, Yosen Whirlwind!

V0504_08_00_25_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Yosenju Oroshi Channeling!

V0504_08_00_26_0.text:
I activate my Quick-Play Spell!
Yosenju Wind Worship!

V0504_08_00_27_0.text:
I activate my Counter Trap!
Yosenjus' Secret Move!

V0504_08_00_28_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Yosenjus' Sword Sting!

V0504_08_00_29_0.text: I activate my Spell Card, Frost Blast of the Monarchs!

V0504_08_00_30_0.text: I activate Frost Blast of the Monarchs from my Graveyard!

V0504_08_00_31_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
The Monarchs Awaken!

V0504_08_00_32_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
The Monarchs Erupt!

V0504_08_00_33_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Dark Advance!

V0504_08_00_34_0.text:
This card's worthless... but oh well!
The Humble Sentry!

V0504_08_00_35_0.text: I activate the Equip Spell, Fairy Meteor Crush!

V0504_08_00_36_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Breakthrough Skill!

V0504_08_00_37_0.text: I activate Breakthrough Skill's effect from my Graveyard!

V0504_08_00_38_0.text:
I bet you don't own a card this rare!
Dark Mirror Force!

V0504_08_00_39_0.text:
I wish I had a better card...
I activate Localized Tornado!

V0504_08_00_40_0.text: I activate Abyss Actor - Superstar's Pendulum Effect!

V0504_08_00_41_0.text: Abyss Actor - Extras' Pendulum Effect activates!

V0504_08_00_42_0.text: I activate Abyss Actor - Evil Heel's Pendulum Effect!

V0504_08_00_43_0.text: I activate Abyss Actor - Funky Comedian's Pendulum Effect!

V0504_08_00_44_0.text: I activate Abyss Actor - Leading Lady's Pendulum Effect!

V0504_08_00_45_0.text: I activate Abyss Actor - Wild Hope's Pendulum Effect!

V0504_08_00_46_0.text: Abyss Actor - Curtain Raiser's Pendulum Effect activates!

V0504_08_00_47_0.text: I activate Abyss Actor - Comic Relief's Pendulum Effect!

V0504_08_00_48_0.text: Abyss Actor - Trendy Understudy's Pendulum Effect activates!

V0504_08_00_49_0.text: I play Abyss Actor - Twinkle Little Star's Pendulum Effect!

V0504_08_00_50_0.text: I activate Abyss Actor - Mellow Madonna's Pendulum Effect!

V0504_08_00_52_0.text: I activate Mayosenju Hitot's Pendulum Effect!

V0504_08_00_53_0.text: I activate Yosenju Shinchu R's effect!

V0504_09_00_00_1.text: I select an Abyss Script in my deck and Set it on my field!

V0504_09_00_15_0.text: I can summon a lot of monsters without Pendulum Summoning!

V0504_09_00_16_0.text: When Yosenju Kama 1 is summoned, its effect activates!

V0504_09_00_18_0.text: When Yosenju Kama 2 is summoned, its effect activates!

V0504_09_00_19_0.text:
Yosenju Kama 2's effect activates!
Come on back!

V0504_09_00_20_0.text: When Yosenju Kama 3 is summoned, its effect activates!

V0504_09_00_23_0.text: You're about to learn how terrifying Pendulum Summon can be!

V0504_09_00_25_0.text: Return to my hand, Yosenju Sabu!

V0504_09_00_26_0.text: Now's not the time to go easy on you!

V0504_09_00_26_1.text: I use Yosenju Oyam's effect to Special Summon it!

V0504_09_00_28_0.text: I activate Yosenju Tsujik's effect from my hand!

V0504_09_00_31_0.text: I banish Yosenju Kodam from my Graveyard to use its effect!

V0504_09_00_33_0.text: I discard Yosenju Izna to activate its effect!

V0504_09_00_35_0.text:
Mobius the Frost Monarch!
Activate your effect!

V0504_09_00_36_0.text: Mobius the Mega Monarch activates its effect!

V0504_09_00_37_0.text: I activate Erebus the Underworld Monarch's effect!

V0504_09_00_38_0.text: I activate Erebus's effect from my Graveyard!

V0504_09_00_39_0.text: I activate Eidos the Underworld Squire's effect!

V0504_09_00_40_0.text: I banish Eidos from my Graveyard to activate its effect!

V0504_09_00_41_0.text: Angmarl the Fiendish Monarch activates its effect!

V0504_09_00_43_0.text:
May as well play Block Spider's effect.
Better than nothing.

V0504_13_00_00_0.text: Allow me to introduce Abyss Actor - Superstar!

V0504_37_00_00_0.text: Behold a beast born from the howls of the winds!

V0504_13_00_13_0.text:
Composed of chaos and cruelty!
Mayosenju Hitot!

V0504_13_00_32_0.text: Only a rare specimen like me deserves to use this rare card!

V0504_13_00_33_0.text: This is one of those special Pendulum Cards!

V0504_13_00_34_0.text: Did I really put this garbage in my deck?

V0504_13_00_35_0.text:
This card is useless!
But I have no choice but to play it...

V0504_13_00_36_1.text: I don't recall putting this lame card in my deck!

V0504_13_00_37_1.text: I'd rather get food poisoning than play a card this weak.

V0504_19_00_00_0.text:
Superstar!
Show 'em how you earned your name!

V0504_19_00_19_0.text: Yosenju Magat! Swirl up a storm!

V0504_19_00_35_0.text:
The Six Samurai - Yariza!
Make yourself useful!

V0504_19_00_37_0.text:
Hungry Burger!
Chomp up that appetizer!

V0504_44_00_02_0.text: Only one will rule the Duel...

V0504_44_00_03_0.text: In the ultimate fusion of monsters and mayhem!
